Additional data on this isotope can be found in [08Ta29, 06Lo04, 05Fr17, 04Fr30, 02Fo03, 02St06,
02We15, 00FoZY, 95Ay03, 86Sa13, 85Co20, 77De30, 75Ip01, 74Ch52, 71Ba43, 70Bi03].
Abundance: 17.15(8) %.
Levels of the ground-state band marked here
a are considered in [05Pa48, 02Fo03].
The first 3 columns contain data on the (t,p) and (d,p) reactions [75Ip01] and the parameter
ε=σ exp /σ DW BA [74Fl02]; recommended data on the deuteron stripping [00Bb11] as S
=(2J f +
1)S/(2J i + 1) [79Bo35] are given next; data on the (α, τ ) reaction [70Bi03] are given separately.
Deformation parameters β L R are in fm units, additional parameters can be found in [86Si17].
Data on the(d,τ ) reaction can be found in [00Bb11, 95Ay03, 74Ch52] (including S N =10.8 for the
ground state).
All data on neutron resonance parameters were not included in NDS [00Bb11].
Data on σ • in the total cross section measured at ORELA are derived from Exfor 13741 [00Ha0A].
Neutron capture in
91 Zr and the resonance parameters were measured in [86Sa13, 86Ma10], the
measured values of J=3, Γ n =665(5) meV and Γ γ =131(7) meV for E • =292 eV confirm the values
from [78Br0A]; resonances at E • =2361 and 2384 were not observed in [00Le01]. Data for this
isotope are considered in vol. LB I/18B.
